div.q:
And thou, O God, shalt bring them down into the Pit of Corruption;
the Bloody and deceitfull men shall not live half their dayes,
Psal. 55. 23.

div.p:
               Inform. His Worship in Spirit and Truth is but the lesser part of his
due. It is obedience God desires rather then Sacrifice or Worship;
God commands you to be obedient to Authority.
